description: Darkness Radio welcomes a man named Nikolai to the program. Nikolai has written a book detailing an experience where he was traveling on a train with his mother, who is a hypnotherapist, when he was young.  Nikolai wanted her to put him into hypnotic regression to see what she could find!  What came out next... was mind blowing!!
